#: units-identity.rst:58
msgid "Entering ``unit`` defines the claim and defines the relevant fields to be used in further data entry about a :ref:`unit`. For quality assurance purposes, entering ``unit`` should create an error if there is any entry for fields tied to other claim types, such as :ref:`positioning` or :ref:`relation`."
msgstr ""

